Details about each resources and its properties can be found here:

https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/aws-template-resource-type-ref.html

For Example to create user wuth cloud formation, properties of use resource are defined here. Please check the "required: yes", If there is any property which is defined as required: yes, then it has to be defined

https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/aws-resource-iam-user.html


